Create vertual env : 
************************
py -m venv <envvname>

activate venev : 
<envname>\script\activate

Install django : 
pip install django

create django project : 
py -m django startproject <projectname> .

run project : 
py manage.py runserver

create app : 
py manage.py startapp <appname>

add app into steeting.py filr under installApp


